Maintainer: Megha Joshi <megha.j456@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides applied meta-analytic researchers a set of functions with which they can conduct single coefficient tests or multiple-contrast hypothesis tests using cluster wild bootstrapping, based on methods examined in Joshi, Pustejovsky, and Beretvas (2021) <DOI: 10.31222/osf.io/x6uhk>. 
